# Keep the Vercel deploy Node-only. These are the repo-root ML/Python artifacts,
# not part of the web build. Every pattern is anchored with a leading slash so it
# ONLY matches the repo root — never frontend/src, frontend/src/data, etc.
# (An unanchored "src/" or "data/" would match those nested dirs and break the build.)
/requirements.txt
/*.ipynb
/.ipynb_checkpoints/
/notebooks/
/models/
/data/
/scripts/
/src/
